          <p>At $70-90, the Wyze Lock Bolt is the most affordable option on this list. It offers fingerprint access and PIN entry, but it runs on Bluetooth only, which means remote access requires a separate hub and guest code management is largely manual. PMS integration is limited compared to WiFi-enabled competitors. Suitable for hosts managing a single listing on a tight budget who don't mind setting codes by hand for each booking.</p>

          <h2 id="what-to-look-for">What to Look For When Choosing a Smart Lock</h2>
